{"tid":2238653,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學生抗爭相展 警稱鼓吹暴力","createTime":"2020-10-11T10:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T10:20:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d553576adf3551dcdd084137a62138628302285b","tid":2238653,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/RADS56V5CRA2JA4OJDYTZKYKWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FRADS56V5CRA2JA4OJDYTZKYKWA%2F&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=1b81de03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FRADS56V5CRA2JA4OJDYTZKYKWA%2F&h=b5c4d2dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/RADS56V5CRA2JA4OJDYTZKYKWA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n學生抗爭相展 警稱鼓吹暴力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tuWHw196ADFXXWVBsnEyfvSKbbg=/1328x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LUWQHNQ425AZ5PPZOFJPX3V6SE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtuWHw196ADFXXWVBsnEyfvSKbbg%3D%2F1328x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLUWQHNQ425AZ5PPZOFJPX3V6SE.jpg&h=186a095c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方昨以橙帶圍封賢學思政街站，指展品鼓吹暴力。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方行動屢次針對學生，昨午學生組織「賢學思政」在銅鑼灣東角道開設街站，舉行「初心──四季不變」抗爭攝影展，呼籲關注12名送中港人情況。期間大批警員拉起橙帶圍封，有警員聲稱收到投訴，指街站展品「鼓吹暴力」，截查成員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n截查10分鐘 便衣全程拍攝<br />\n<br />\n賢學思政召集人王逸戰曾質問警員哪一張照片鼓吹暴力，但對方沒回答，僅稱日後或檢控他。。。。。。。。。。。。。。街站最終在警員監察下提早20分鐘結束。<br />\n<br />\n王逸戰認為展出的是正常新聞照片，質疑警方指控街站鼓吹暴力是白色恐怖，「或許香港喺國安法之下可以做嘅嘢越嚟越少，我哋都俾人打壓，但我哋面對嘅遠不及12位港人。」他強調不會放棄，未來在不同戰線努力。攝影展昨日至10月25日期間在朗屏、西環、旺角等多區舉行。"},{"pid":"7d9eca9c044eec8992282551ecfa7d425288dbf4","tid":2238653,"uid":121197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"有警察嘅樣=鼓吹暴力"},{"pid":"e2761c95feb400d22a32839ef59f30326afa47da","tid":2238653,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d9eca9c044eec8992282551ecfa7d425288dbf4","tid":2238653,"uid":121197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"有警察嘅樣=鼓吹暴力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}